line_1: Or else imperfect were the rites of funeral.
line_2: And near it rosemary climbs up the wall;

line_1: Or write a Poem on his Funeral?
line_2: But what vile Bard will e'er lament his Fall,

line_1: The Tears you'l give my Funeral,
line_2: Will pay me Int'rest, Stock and all.

line_1: And wonder at the sudden funeral.
line_2: A train of mourning friends attend his pall,
